CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 23, 1966, pg. 3A reads: "Health-O-Rama Scenes - The United Fund sponsored Health-O-Rama last week at the Savoy Ballroom in the Hill District attracted a large crowd of those eager to keep in top physical condition. From left to right -- Mary Bailey pricks the finger of Darnel Taylor, while little Dino Johnson looks on.  At the right Mary Lou Thomas waits her turn as does Delores Johnson in the background (far right.) - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Mary Bailey pricking finger of Darnel Taylor, with Dino Johnson looking on, and Mary Lou Thomas and Delores Johnson waiting on right, at booth in Savoy Ballroom for United Fund's Health-O-Rama
